{
  "stem": "13313.4",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, what happened was that the, the elation of this moment, between being liberated and having my parents back against all the odds-- it must have been very-- there were very, very few families that were fortunate enough to have both parents and both children, because my uncle's and aunts weren't all that fortunate.",
      "word_count": 54
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My uncle Jacques never came back from Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He didn't jump from the train.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "His wife, Rochelle or Rachel, and her little boy-- they had a little daughter that was born in 1940.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So she  was only two years old when all this started.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they managed to put her in hiding with an elderly couple.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But the wife was caught with the, with the child.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "My aunt Rosa was caught with the two children.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "My mother went to give her food.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "All the-- they never came back.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They're all gone.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Rosette.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Unfortunately, the people that hid her-- so my father found her, through-- because now the community organized to locate people-- try and find kids in that were in hiding, that were baptized, kids that-- tried to unite family members from all over the place.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Few people had survived.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And so we found Rosette.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Now, she had the same name as my father, so my father right away made arrangements to take Rosette in.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And as far as she was concerned, she was very weak.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "She was absolutely a physical wreck.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Unfortunate-- I hate to say this-- but those older people turned out to be a pair of perverts.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And she was sleeping with them in their own beds and what they did with her-- this kid was absolutely a psychological and physical wreck.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "She couldn't even walk.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
